}, {\"ngram\": \"her 17th career Paralympic gold medal\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To come back three years later -and it's been a really tough three years - to swim this race and to somehow get on the podium and win gold, it's unimaginable,\\\" she said on TODAY on Sept. 5.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really tough three years\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"TODAY\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"Sept.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is so much work that went into it.\\\"\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much work\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Long, 32, has now won the 400 freestyle - S8 race four times in her Paralympic career, having also captured the gold in 2004, 2008 and 2012.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 400 freestyle - S8 race\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"her Paralympic career\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels unreal and heavy, very heavy,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This one is so special to me.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This one\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I definitely wanted to get to that 30 mark, and the gold is just so, so sweet.\\\"\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that 30 mark\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimming star overtook T